dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Title cartouche has lambs' heads and is topped by British coat of arms flanked by a catlike dragon and a lion wearing a crown. Includes ships and sea monsters in the ocean. Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt. From the Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map: 33 x 45 cm.
